
 

 How to Automatically Revert  Changes on Ec2 Security Groups
 ********************************************************************

1)  Create Custom VPC Security Group with tag name Name:prod-sg 

2) Create Cloud Trail on the Region

3) Create Lambda execution role with ec2 permission

4) Create Lambda funtion and add which security group need for revert changes

5) Add Cloudwatch Event Trigger for security group changes

6) Test : change the rule in the securiry group
